Commands create a bootable Ubuntu USB flash drive:
first format and umount USB then
method1:
	 sudo dd if=input.iso of=/dev/sdb
method2:
	sudo cat input.iso > /dev/sdb
_______________________________________________________________________________

dpkg -s <package name> - gives all necessory details

_______________________________________________________________________________
connecting wifi through commandline

nmcli dev wifi list
nmcli dev wifi connect "SSID" password "PASSWORD"
